  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 Orthopedic — Tibial Tray Contact Stress Credibility Assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for finite element prediction of tibial tray contact stress in a total knee arthroplasty (TKA) implant under physiological loading. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict peak contact stress and stress distribution across the tibial plateau for a Class II orthopedic device at Model Risk Level 3. All 13 credibility factors are fully assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels at MRL 3. Decision: Accepted.",
